Class GovernanceActionRequestBody

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.gaf.rest.GovernanceActionRequestBody
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class GovernanceActionRequestBody extends Object implements Serializable
GovernanceActionRequestBody provides a structure for passing the properties for a new governance action.
